---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <title>STS S.A.C. | Especialistas en Llantas Industriales y Agrícolas</title>
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased text-slate-900">
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-gray-200 py-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <img src="/logo-sts.png" alt="STS Logo" class="h-10 w-auto">
                <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tighter text-blue-900">STS S.A.C.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 font-medium">
                <a href="#inicio" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Inicio</a>
                <a href="#sectores" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Sectores</a>
                <a href="#catalogo" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Catálogo</a>
                <a href="#nosotros" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Nosotros</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wa.me/51958322241?text=Hola%20STS,%20vengo%20de%20la%20web" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-md font-bold text-sm hover:bg-red-700 transition">COTIZAR</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="inicio" class="relative h-screen flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img 
                src="/hero-sts.jpg" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-[0.4]" 
                alt="Maquinaria pesada STS"
            >
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <span class="text-red-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 block underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">Confianza y Rendimiento</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
                    Llantas para los terrenos más <span class="text-red-600">exigentes.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                    Especialistas en sectores Agrícola, Industrial, OTR y Transporte Pesado. Asesoría profesional y despacho a nivel nacional.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="#catalogo" class="bg-white text-blue-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-center hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Ver Catálogo PDF</a>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/51958322241" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-center hover:bg-red-700 transition">Asesoría Inmediata</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="sectores" class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Soluciones por Sector</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Contamos con neumáticos diseñados para maximizar la productividad de su operación.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
                <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">A</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Agrícola</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm italic">Tractores y maquinaria de campo.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 bg-blue-900 text-white">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">I</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Industrial & OTR</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm italic">Minería y construcción.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">C</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Camión & Bus</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm italic">Transporte de carga pesada.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-200">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <p class="text-center text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Distribuidores de Marcas Globales</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 opacity-60 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-500">
                <span class="text-2xl font-black">MICHELIN</span>
                <span class="text-2xl font-black">BRIDGESTONE</span>
                <span class="text-2xl font-black">GOODYEAR</span>
                <span class="text-2xl font-black">TRIANGLE</span>
                <span class="text-2xl font-black">BKT</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="catalogo" class="py-24 bg-blue-950 text-white relative">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 italic">¿Busca especificaciones técnicas?</h2>
                <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Nuestro portafolio actualizado incluye todas las medidas, índices de carga y diseños de banda de rodamiento.
                </p>
                <ul class="mb-10 space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span> Precios competitivos</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span> Garantía de fábrica</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✓</span> Despacho nacional</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/catalogo-sts.pdf" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-900 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition transform">
                    DESCARGAR CATÁLOGO (PDF)
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
                <img src="/almacen-sts.jpg" class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-white/10 w-full h-auto" alt="Almacén STS">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="nosotros" class="bg-white pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-gray-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-2xl text-blue-900 mb-6 uppercase">STS S.A.C.</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">Aliados estratégicos en el sector, garantizando profesionalismo, ética y moral en cada venta.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Ubicaciones</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-2">📍 <strong>Cañete:</strong> Jr. Garro 280, San Vicente.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">📍 <strong>Lima:</strong> Atención y despacho a nivel nacional.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Contacto Directo</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">📧 ventas@stsllantas.com</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">📞 958 322 241 / 966 022 790</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">🏢 RUC: 20606471853</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center text-gray-400 text-sm border-t border-gray-50 pt-10">
                &copy; 2026 STS S.A.C. - Todos los derechos reservados.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>